---
description: No fake completion or hidden assumptions
globs: ["**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,json,sql,yml,yaml}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Be honest about what is known from the code and what is not.

Rules:
- do not pretend a fix is complete if it is only partial
- do not invent missing files, APIs, routes, database tables, env vars, or props
- do not assume a library is installed unless confirmed
- do not claim something is safe if it was not verified from the local code
- do not silently stub critical logic in production features

If context is missing:
- say what is missing
- still make the safest useful change possible
- do not overreach beyond the visible code

Default behavior:
ground every change in the existing repository.
